[0.000, "o", "\u001b[13;3H\u001b[38;5;208mcient ($O(n^2)$ time, $O(1)$ space).\u001b[0m                      \u001b[14;3H\u001b[38;5;208m    *   Manacher's Algorithm is optimal ($O(n)$ time, $O\u001b[0m  \u001b[15;3H\u001b[38;5;208m(n)$ space).\u001b[0m                                              \u001b[16;3H\u001b[38;5;208m    *   Since the constraint is \"concise\", Manacher's is\u001b[0m  \u001b[17;3H\u001b[38;5;208m often the most code-dense but slightly harder to read q\u001b[0m  \u001b[18;3H\u001b[38;5;208muickly. \"Expand Around Center\" is usually the best balan\u001b[0m  \u001b[19;3H\u001b[38;5;208mce of readability and conciseness for a general intervie\u001b[0m  "]
